S01E01 300 Feet Below
First aired: 9/19/1964 
The victim of a shark attack, Dr. Bill Darmon, is far out to sea and needs an immediate blood transfusion. Flipper retrieves the plasma from the bottom of the sea when it is dropped from a helicopter.

Regular Cast: Brian Kelly as Porter Ricks, Luke Halpin as Sandy Ricks, Tommy Norden as "Bud" Ricks, Andy Devine as Hap Gorman

Guest cast: Bob Sipes as Helicopter Crew Chief, Bill Traylor as Dr. Darmon (as William Traylor), Jessica Walter as Elena Darmon.

S01E02 The Red Hot Car
First aired: 9/26/1964 
Sandy and Bud discover a bullet-riddled car at the bottom of the bay. Disobeying their father, they dive down to investigate. When criminals try to blow the car up with the boys trapped inside, Flipper comes to the rescue and the criminals are taken by the police.
